OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FDuring an inquest at Leicester City
OL,8,FHall on Tuesday, a jury heard that two
OL,9,Fpolice officers used a baton and fire
OL,10,Fextinguisher to try to save Khun
OL,11,FVichai, pilot Eric Swaffer, his
OL,12,Fpartner Izabela Lechowicz, and
OL,13,Fpassengers Nusara Suknamai and
OL,14,FKaveporn Punpare.
OL,16,FSergeant Mike Hooper and Constable
OL,17,FStephen Quartermain of Leicestershire
OL,18,FPolice were patrolling nearby in a
OL,19,Fmarked vehicle when they saw the
OL,20,Fhelicopter start to rotate and heard a
OL,21,F"loud crunch" as it hit the ground.
OL,26,@}D@AOU}D@MO]
