OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FPc Quartermain told the inquest he saw
OL,8,Fthree people trapped in the back of
OL,9,Fthe aircraft who were "moving their
OL,10,Farms and legs around".
OL,12,FDescribing the pilot he said: "He was
OL,13,Flooking at me but not reacting. I
OL,14,Fdidn't know whether he was
OL,15,Funconscious, but certainly
OL,16,Funresponsive at that point."
OL,18,F"The flames started to take to the
OL,19,Frear of the aircraft. It was at that
OL,20,Fpoint I realised the people were going
OL,21,Fto die", he added tearfully.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@UO]tD@_OUxD@\O]zD@AOU
