OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FBoth officers told the hearing the
OL,8,Fpilot had been shouting "get me out of
OL,9,Fhere, help me".
OL,11,FLeicestershire Fire and Rescue station
OL,12,Fmanager Chris Parsons told the inquest
OL,13,Fit would have been a "significant
OL,14,Fchallenge" and "potentially not
OL,15,Fpossible" without time to extinguish
OL,16,Fthe fire.
