OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FPhilip Shepherd KC, representing the
OL,8,Frelatives of Khun Vichai, told the
OL,9,Fofficers: "On behalf of the family of
OL,10,FKhun Vichai can I congratulate you on
OL,11,Fthe heroic efforts you made that night
OL,12,Fto try to save the lives of the people
OL,13,Fwho tragically died."
OL,15,FJohn Ledwidge, former grounds manager
OL,16,Fat Leicester City, told the inquest he
OL,17,Fsaw the moment the aircraft caught
OL,18,Ffire after it "aggressively" spun to
OL,19,Fthe ground.
