OL,7,FHe added that club owner Khun Vichai
OL,8,Fwas an "investor in people's dreams",
OL,9,Fadding, "he touched a lot of people
OL,10,Fwith his generosity, his warmth and
OL,11,Fhumour. I felt like I was part of the
OL,12,Ffamily."
